    @Reference(authors="C. H. Ang and T. C. Tan",
           title="New linear node splitting algorithm for R-trees",
           booktitle="Proceedings of the 5th International Symposium on Advances in Spatial Databases",

public class AngTanLinearSplit
extends Object
implements SplitStrategy
    Line-time complexity split proposed by Ang and Tan. This split strategy tries to minimize overlap only, which can however degenerate to "slices".

    C. H. Ang and T. C. Tan:
    New linear node splitting algorithm for R-trees
    In: Proceedings of the 5th International Symposium on Advances in Spatial Databases

    Since:
    0.5.0
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
